{"id":546993,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/【麻辣总局】发现雾霾源头/","date":"2016-12-19T08:26:45Z","modified":"2016-12-19T08:26:45Z","title":"【麻辣总局】发现雾霾源头","content":"<p>@风中疾走：肥肠有道理，可能发现了雾霾的一个源头。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/59479230gw1faupufg8snj20jz0zk40m.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-546994\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/59479230gw1faupufg8snj20jz0zk40m.jpg\" alt=\"59479230gw1faupufg8snj20jz0zk40m\" width=\"450\" height=\"801\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/59479230gw1faupufg8snj20jz0zk40m.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/59479230gw1faupufg8snj20jz0zk40m-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/59479230gw1faupufg8snj20jz0zk40m-575x1024.jpg 575w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@meimzle：完蛋！我车号是单号！罪恶感太强！</p>\n<p>@安心ARS：摆事实讲道理。</p>\n<p>@跟疯小胖墩：原来烧烤摊是被冤枉的！</p>\n<p>@Paul郑褚 ：北京的pm2.5究竟谁是源头：冬天烧煤是罪魁祸首。汽车排放对空气污染影响大不大：大，但私家车影响不大，汽车污染的90%是柴油大货车造成的，这就是为什么国外大城市汽车密度高于中国却没听说有雾霾。那为什么治霾总是拿私家车开刀：因为欺负你们比较容易。你看，三句话就说清楚了。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,13789],"tags":[26566,22350,21969,32120,22409,27146,9151,9014,16291,10829,10582,10510,21943,22221,22011,12979]}